info.longDescription: Neo Dental Clinic is a state-of-the-art dental clinic and laboratory located in Tirana. Our clinic specializes in oral implantology, aesthetic dentistry and orthodontics. We have been providing high-quality dental treatments for 10 years with the utmost care for our patients, always using the best quality materials.
